Instructions to run GNU Radio Companion with Red Pitaya

Cloning the source code repository:

  git clone https://github.com/pavel-demin/red-pitaya-notes
  cd red-pitaya-notes/projects/sdr_transceiver_hpsdr/gnuradio

Running example SSB transceiver:

  export GRC_BLOCKS_PATH=.
  gnuradio-companion trx_ssb.grc

